summary: My config file for Skyrim Community Uncapper tailored for Skyrim Redone
descriptionHtml:
Uploading mainly so I don\'t loose it but hopefully someone else will enjoy it as much as I am. Be warned, it\'s pretty unforgiving. Choices matter more but happen less often, every other level until 10, then every 5 levels until 50/60 then every 10 levels capping out at 100.

Required mods (you REALLY should be using these anyways) :
Skyrim -Community- Uncapper by Elys -http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/1175
T3nd0s Skyrim Redone by T3nd0 - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/9286

Recommended mods :
Deadly Dragons by 3JIou - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3829
Dragon Soul Relinquishment by Alek - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/27531
Enhanced High-Level Gameplay by Eric - http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14449
author: Colony
